data.description: COMING SOON! This home priced for quick sale, so seller took that into consideration and says to sell sold AS IS…home offers a great  floor plan for the family that likes to entertain! (Notice the beautiful wood floors) Walk into the foyer & you have this great open/ sunken living room w vaulted ceiling & fireplace! On main level off foyer is a room that can be used as an office/extra bedroom. Huge kitchen w pantry/LOTS of cabinets/island. Off kitchen is a large covered deck & above ground pool/fenced yard. 3+ bedrooms/2 ba. One of the bedrooms offers a huge 10x10 walk-in closet or can be used as sitting room. 2 car garage. Basement has some finish.
